    Interface Description
    Category
    Interface Category
    A public type to organize part types in categories

    Interface CompatibilityChecker
    A public type to get constraints (requirements and incompatibilities)
    for a specific PartType
    CompatibilityManager
    Interface CompatibilityManager
    A public type to get manage (add and remove) constraints between parts
    Configuration
    Interface Configuration
    Represent a configuration chosen by the customer
    Check the state of a configuration, select and unselect parts

    _ variant
    _ configuration
    _ compatibilityChecker objects
    Part
    Interface that represents a Part with properties
    PartType
    Interface of PartType

    Allows to get the characteristics of a PartType
    PropertyManager
    Add properties to a object
    Visitor
    Visitor interface for the prettyPrinter
